1
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:47,440
Lingling,

2
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:49,520
what are you thinking about?

3
00:00:50,600 --> 00:00:51,760
My mom was beaten.

4
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:55,640
By whom?

5
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:57,850
Let's go. I'll get revenge for you.

6
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:00,120
By your dad.

7
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:04,879
Impossible.

8
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,360
You must be mistaken.

9
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:07,640
My dad has such a good temper.

10
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,680
How could he hit someone?

11
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:10,010
I saw it with my own eyes.

12
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:11,880
When I went to see my mom,

13
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:12,560
your dad's hand

14
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,960
landed right on her face.

15
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:16,050
Later, after your dad left,

16
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:17,360
I put medicine on her.

17
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,160
I saw on her body

18
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:20,800
and arms,

19
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,660
they were covered in bruises.

20
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:24,640
Your dad definitely didn't just

21
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:25,500
hit my mom once.

22
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,440
Lingling.

23
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:28,400
I know

24
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,280
you're a bit emotional right now,

25
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:34,200
but there must be some misunderstanding.

26
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:34,920
My dad couldn't...

27
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:37,120
What misunderstanding could there be?

28
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:40,680
Your dad shouldn't have hit her.

29
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:44,920
You don't believe me.

30
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:50,640
Then what do you want me to do?

31
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:55,720
If you insist on standing by your dad,

32
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,320
then we are enemies.

33
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,400
One is my father, and the other is you.

34
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:09,199
Forcing me to make a choice.

35
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:16,800
Ruan Nila.

36
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:18,520
Stop.

37
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:21,760
Stop right there.

38
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,130
Chen Angwei.

39
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,520
Go.

40
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:29,480
Ruan Nila.

41
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:33,280
I have evidence of your hallucinogens.

42
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,410
If you let her go now,

43
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:37,300
I won't hand it over to the police.

44
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:39,240
That way you still have a way out.

45
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,000
Ang Wei.

46
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,920
You finally came back for her.

47
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,680
Whatever you say now,

48
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,650
do you think I'd still care?

49
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,640
Take one more step,

50
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:51,880
and I'll let her taste

51
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:53,440
this tenfold hallucinogen.

52
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,040
Ruan Nila.

53
00:02:57,079 --> 00:02:58,410
As long as you let her go,

54
00:02:59,360 --> 00:02:59,880
I'll do whatever you ask.

55
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:00,480
I promise.

56
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:09,960
Put the gun down.

57
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,520
Throw the files over.

58
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,650
Don't listen to her.

59
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,100
Get out of here.

60
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:25,720
Leave quickly, Angwei.

61
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:26,280
Shut up.

62
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:33,050
Tell the dogs behind you

63
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,320
to handcuff themselves.

64
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,660
Sit over there.

65
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,720
All of you, leave.

66
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:09,320
Angwei,

67
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:12,060
you finally came to beg me.

68
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,800
For this woman,

69
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,040
you came to beg me.

70
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,360
Look at you now.

71
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,920
Where did all your previous arrogance

72
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,920
towards me go?

73
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:34,920
Tell me.

74
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,080
Why did you choose her over me?

75
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:37,640
Shut up.

76
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:39,800
Ruan Nila.

77
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:43,170
Do you know what you are saying?

78
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,000
Angwei.

79
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:46,360
I know you always report on me

80
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,400
to the master.

81
00:04:48,159 --> 00:04:49,690
But I have never blamed you.

82
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:54,880
You know.

83
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,780
You have always known that I love you.

84
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,320
Angwei.

85
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:03,960
Just say it once.

86
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:07,360
Can you just say you love me for once?

87
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,640
You make me sick.

88
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:11,880
What exactly do you want?

89
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:22,920
Bitch.

90
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,720
You are all bitches.

91
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:27,680
Fine.

92
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,930
You like her, don't you?

93
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,440
I'll grant your wish now.

94
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,520
You two can stay together

95
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:35,840
and go to hell.

96
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:43,880
Bitch.

97
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,159
I will kill you!

98
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:52,409
Dailing, watch out!

99
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,320
Angwei,

100
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,360
where are you?

101
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,120
Angwei.

102
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,440
Do you know

103
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,760
how much I love you?

104
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:26,700
Where is

105
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:27,920
that bitch?

106
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:30,840
That bitch.

107
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:32,920
I love you

108
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,500
more than that bitch does,

109
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:35,920
a hundred times,

110
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,620
a thousand times more.

111
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,360
Why didn't you choose me?

112
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,240
I, Ruannila,

113
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,360
have everything.

114
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,000
Being with me

115
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:49,280
is your blessing.

116
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,080
Angwei.

117
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,560
Who do you think you are?

118
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:15,920
Danpa is not your biological father at all.

119
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,600
She overdosed on hallucinogens.

120
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:23,260
Don't listen to her nonsense.

121
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:24,920
Tangong.

122
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:29,360
There's a secret hidden in the Tangong Buddhist hall.

123
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:32,640
You brought this upon yourself.

124
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,080
Master.

125
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:10,640
Mrs. Ruan,

126
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:12,520
she is dead.

127
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:14,760
Dead?

128
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,860
How did she die?

129
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:19,440
They said

130
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:20,900
it was a drug overdose.

131
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,290
Before she died,

132
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:25,520
the last people she saw were the young master and Dailing.

133
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,240
Ang Wei.

134
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:32,340
You are really something.

135
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:49,620
Are you worried about something?

136
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:54,490
Danpa used to bring me here to play tennis.

137
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:57,480
I was thinking

138
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:01,090
about what Ruannila said before she died,

139
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,640
that there is a secret about me

140
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:04,440
in the Buddhist hall of Tangong.

141
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:06,770
I don't know if it's true or not.

142
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,680
Before Ruannila died,

143
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:11,280
she was given a large amount of hallucinogens.

144
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,160
Maybe

145
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:15,970
she just wanted to turn you and Danpa against each other.

146
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,500
Maybe I'm just overthinking.

147
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:33,890
Do you want to go?

148
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,560
Then I'll go with you.

149
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,410
Under the Buddha statue

150
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:17,700
is indeed a good place to hide things.

151
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,560
My birthday.

152
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:57,340
The adopter guarantees to fulfill the obligation of raising the adoptee during the adoption period.

153
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,800
So you found out.

154
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:12,280
After raising you for so many years,

155
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:15,050
I still raised a useless, ungrateful wretch.

156
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:16,680
Master.

157
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:17,760
Then we...

158
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:22,480
It's time to meet the newcomers.
